### Create Artist
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/artists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Artist 2",
  "biography": "A test artist for API testing 2."
}

### Get All Artists
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/artists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Artist by ID (replace 1 with actual artist ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/artists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Artist (replace 1 with actual artist ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/artists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Artist Name",
  "biography": "Updated biography"
}

### Delete Artist (replace 1 with actual artist ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/artists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}